8. A capacitor, comprising: 
a bottom plate electrode; 
a tantalum oxynitride film on the bottom plate electrode; 
a thin silicon film on the tantalum oxynitride film; and 
a top plate electrode on the thin silicon film.

22. A capacitor, comprising: 
a bottom plate electrode; 
a tantalum oxynitride film on the bottom plate electrode; 
a thin silicon film on the tantalum oxynitride film; and 
a top plate electrode on the thin silicon film, the top plate electrode containing a material selected from a group consisting of titanium nitride and tungsten nitride.

36. A memory, comprising: 
a memory array having a plurality of capacitors, each capacitor including: 
a bottom plate electrode; 
a tantalum oxynitride film on the bottom plate electrode; 
a thin silicon film on the tantalum oxynitride film; and 
a top plate electrode on the thin silicon film; 

a control circuit, operatively coupled to the memory array; and 
address logic, operatively coupled to the memory array and the control circuit.

